# Copy to .env.local and fill in. The app runs in "demo mode" without these,
# but the REAL AI tutor + translation need Vercel AI Gateway auth.

# Vercel AI Gateway (required for live AI tutor + translation). Get a key at
# https://vercel.com/<team>/<project>/settings/ai — or run `vercel env pull`
# on a linked project to provision VERCEL_OIDC_TOKEN automatically instead.
AI_GATEWAY_API_KEY=...

# Optional model overrides — any Gateway "provider/model" slug works here,
# e.g. openai/gpt-5.4, google/gemini-3-flash, deepseek/deepseek-v3.2:
# AI_MODEL=anthropic/claude-opus-4.8
# AI_TRANSLATE_MODEL=anthropic/claude-sonnet-5

# Supabase (Phase 1 — real auth, roles, and dashboards; see
# supabase/migrations/0001_init.sql for the schema). The app runs exactly as
# it does today — fully open, mock-data dashboards — until both
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ vars below are set.
#
# Google/Microsoft sign-in must ALSO be enabled as providers in the Supabase
# dashboard (Authentication > Providers) — that's where the actual Google
# Cloud / Microsoft Entra OAuth app credentials go; nothing about which
# providers are enabled lives in this app's code or env vars.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://xxxx.supabase.co
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=...
#
# Needed for first-time sign-in to provision a public.users row (bypasses
# RLS — see src/lib/supabase/admin.ts). Keep this out of the client bundle;
# it's never prefixed NEXT_PUBLIC_.
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=...
#
# Which school new sign-ins get provisioned into — every school is a single
# pilot for now (see ROADMAP.md's Phase 2 sequencing), so there's no
# multi-school onboarding flow yet. Must match a real row's id in the
# schools table.
# DEFAULT_SCHOOL_ID=...

# Sentry (error tracking). Both no-op — nothing is initialized — until set.
# SENTRY_DSN=https://...@o0.ingest.sentry.io/0
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SENTRY_DSN=https://...@o0.ingest.sentry.io/0

# Langfuse (LLM observability — traces every /api/tutor and /api/translate
# call). No-ops until both keys are set. Get them from a Langfuse project's
# Settings > API Keys.
# LANGFUSE_PUBLIC_KEY=pk-lf-...
# LANGFUSE_SECRET_KEY=sk-lf-...
# LANGFUSE_BASE_URL=https://cloud.langfuse.com
